Managing Data with Tables Video
    managing_table_starter.xlsx
    Select everything from top to bottom
        CTRL A
    Create table
        Insert -> Create Table
    Delete column
        Right click top of column -> Delete
    Insert column
        Right click top of column -> Insert (goes to left of column chosen)
    Filter
        Click column dropdown -> Deselect what you want -> Press okay
    Unfilter 
        Click column dropdown -> Clear filter
    Custom Sort
        Editing -> Sort & Filter -> Custom Sort -> Sort by -> Then by (sort within a sort)
    Formatting
        Number (probably defaults as General) -> whatever necessary
        Decimal buttons to left and right

